        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "\\u2757 This update requires the reformatting of user data. If you run into any issues or have lost any data, please create an issue on the GitHub. \\u2757",
          "target": "\\\\u2757 此更新需要重新格式化用户数据。如果您遇到任何问题或丢失任何数据，请在GitHub上创建一个问题。 \\\\u2757"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "\\u{1F4C2} Views: You can switch between different views, each with its own set of tasks. This makes it easy to separate work-related to-dos from personal tasks.",
          "target": "\\\\u{1F4C2} 视图：您可以在不同视图之间切换，每个视图都有自己的任务集。这使得将工作相关的待办事项与个人任务分开变得容易。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "\\u270F\\uFE0F Editing tasks & subjects: Update names, due dates, and files.",
          "target": "\\\\u270F\\\\uFE0F 编辑任务和主题：更新名称、截止日期和文件。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "\\u{1F500} Reordering tasks: Arrange tasks the way you like.",
          "target": "\\\\u{1F500} 重新排序任务：按您喜欢的方式排列任务。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "\\u{1F4CC} Auto-sorting subjects: Subjects can now automatically sort to the top based on the number of tasks they have. This feature can be enabled in the settings.",
          "target": "\\\\u{1F4CC} 主题自动排序：主题现在可以根据其拥有的任务数量自动排序到顶部。此功能可在设置中启用。"
        },
        {
